title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Jun 9 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Jun 9 2022
description:
Clay and Buck dissect Biden on Kimmel. Buck says, "Jimmy Kimmel, he should stick to jokes about flatulence." Joy Behar thinks black people don't have guns. Clay says again that he thinks she is the dumbest person commenting on politics on television. Mark Morgan, former acting commissioner of Customs and Border Protection during the Trump administration, joins C&B to react to Biden’s lawless border. DeSantis defends press secretary against WaPo smear.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
